# Force LF on checkout for all text files so a Windows clone (even with
# core.autocrlf=true) cannot rewrite LF->CRLF and corrupt the shebang of the
# bin/* shell scripts or the .bashrc snippets this guide distributes.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Belt-and-suspenders for the executable scripts that rely on a clean shebang.
bin/* text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
